urlText: Special Events - Saturday 24 February
content:
Taylor Swift | The Eras Tour - Accor Stadium, Sydney Olympic Park
18:20 to 23:00
- Valid pre-purchased tickets include travel on Sydney Trains, Sydney Bus, Sydney Olympic Park Major Event Buses, Sydney Metro and Light Rail services.
- The closest station to the venue is Olympic Park. From the station, it's a short 10 minute walk via Olympic Boulevarde to the stadium.
- From Central, express trains will run to Olympic Park from 15:30 onwards stopping at Redfern, Strathfield then Olympic Park.
- Trains also run regularly to Lidcombe where you can head to Platform Zero for a direct train to Olympic Park, running every 10 minutes until late.
- After the concert, express trains will travel to the City and Western Line stations until late.

Blink 182 - Qudos Bank Arena, Sydney Olympic Park
19:30 to 22:15
- The closest station to the venue is Olympic Park.
- Extra services are running from the City and Western Line stations.

Sydney Gay & Lesbian Mardi Gras Bondi Beach Party - Bondi Beach, Bondi
14:00 to 22:00
- The closest station to Bondi Beach is Bondi Junction on the T4 Eastern Suburbs & Illawarra Line. 
- From Bondi Junction catch one of the many shuttle buses running to the beach.

For details, please check https://transportnsw.info/events/2024/02

content:
